      "name": "Bruno",
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 26,
      "isLocalGuide": true,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVudM2y6MCup5PSbG2Klje4ErjXHsPdB3r4bRP-QrX5LBWZF9znOg=s1920-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
      "text": "Absolutely Outstanding Experience!\n\nI recently had the pleasure of visiting SMP Miami Scalp Elite, and I can't say enough good things about my experience. From the moment I walked in, I was greeted with warmth and professionalism. The team is incredibly skilled and knowledgeable, making me feel comfortable and confident throughout the entire process.\n\nThe results are nothing short of amazing! My scalp looks natural and full, and I've received countless compliments. The attention to detail and precision in their work is truly impressive. If you're considering scalp micropigmentation, look no further than SMP Miami Scalp Elite. They are simply the best in the business!\n\nThank you, SMP Miami Scalp Elite (Maxime) for giving me my confidence back!",
      "textTranslated": "Pengalaman yang Sangat Luar Biasa!\n\nBaru-baru ini saya berkesempatan mengunjungi SMP Miami Scalp Elite, dan saya tidak bisa berkata-kata betapa puasnya saya dengan pengalaman ini. Sejak saya masuk, saya disambut dengan hangat dan profesional. Timnya sangat terampil dan berpengetahuan luas, membuat saya merasa nyaman dan percaya diri sepanjang prosesnya.\n\nHasilnya sungguh menakjubkan! Kulit kepala saya terlihat alami dan lebat, dan saya menerima banyak pujian. Perhatian terhadap detail dan ketelitian dalam pekerjaan mereka benar-benar mengesankan. Jika Anda mempertimbangkan mikropigmentasi kulit kepala, jangan ragu lagi, pilihlah SMP Miami Scalp Elite. Mereka adalah yang terbaik di bidangnya!\n\nTerima kasih, SMP Miami Scalp Elite (Maxime) karena telah mengembalikan kepercayaan diri saya!",
      "publishAt": "2 tahun lalu",
      "publishedAtDate": "2024-07-06T20:39:47.724Z",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "reviewId": "ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNyMXZpcjlBRRAB",
